ml_tags: In Loving Memory Of 10/02/1905 - 15/10/1949 Jajja Isaya Kyankya You passed away when your youngest child, Rose Mary Dawson, was very young, but the love that she had for you still lives on  in her children and grandchildren. Although we never knew you, you will always hold a special place in our hearts. Grace Dawson, Mukibi James and Family With the fondest love
